    "Body": "Lead Brand Designer New York, NY or Remote / Design & Product / Full-Time Apply for this job Blockstack is software for a user-owned internet. It\u2019s the easiest way to build decentralized apps that can scale. Core protocols for Blockstack are developed as open-source and there are 400+ independent apps on the network. Blockstack PBC is a leading entity within the Stacks Ecosystem, advancing the initial research and development of the Stacks Blockchain and developer tools for decentralized applications. The mission of the open-source community and broader ecosystem is to provide software for a user owned internet that returns online data ownership to developers and consumers.???????????? Blockstack PBC was founded in 2013 and is headquartered in New York City with employees and contractors in Canada, Europe, and Asia, Blockstack PBC is funded and backed by more than $75 million from Union Square Ventures, Y Combinator, Lux Capital, Winklevoss Capital, Naval Ravikant, and many more. More info here. Blockstack is looking for a Lead Brand Designer to own all branded communications within the Blockstack ecosystem. In this role, you\u2019ll have the opportunity to rebrand the Blockstack ecosystem, and unify our branded assets across various products, campaigns, and web properties, such as: Blockstack.org, Stackstoken.com, App.co, Blockstack explorer,???????????? What you'll do:???????????? \u2022 Lead a generalized rebrand of the Blockstack ecosystem. \u2022 Lead continuous upgrades and redesign of our key web properties.???????????? \u2022 Partner with our CEO, growth, and marketing teams to produce campaigns, presentations, and live event materials.???????????? \u2022 Partner with our product team to unify branding across our applications.???????????? \u2022 Own concept through production for all branded communications. What we're looking for: \u2022 Design leader with experience from industry leading technology startups.???????????? \u2022 History of c